{
  "stem": "21437.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And outside, we were just nobody.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I didn't mind to go down the street and to be a nobody.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But oh, no.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I mean, I was not allowed to, you know?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I had to put up with this.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And after a while, if I walked with a friend, this sometimes we try to arrange this.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But as it was so far and we didn't talk on the phone like we do now-- we had the telephone, but I wouldn't think, you know, to ring to my friends because most of them didn't.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So we just-- if we just happened to meet by chance, it was better.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But if you were on your own, if you can imagine, to walk down the street and through-- to-- from far, I could see, oh, ho.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "There aer about 10 or 12 of them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Big fat bullies, you know?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So it was-- I somehow-- I don't know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Perhaps something in my-- in that my stance, or something in the way I held myself.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "That after a while it was not so painful.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And after a while, I was not as vulnerable.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "What did the bullies do?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Called me names.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Pushed me.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I wouldn't.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I didn't even want to know their names.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What they called me mainly, those names.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[POLISH].",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That I am fat.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That I am ugly.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Anything they could think of.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But what I realize now-- I mean, it was so brutal, you know.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But what I realize, that they were really children, and this is what they've learned on their grandparents' knees.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So you-- you know, they've learned to-- to adore-- to worship Hitler.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They've learned all the, you know, warfare.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "About all of this.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
